                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7780" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0211</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">64621 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿孔雀叫停，39亿元水电站何去何从？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Where will the 3.9 billion yuan hydropower station go when the green peacock calls a halt?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李斌，王静</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京物资学院</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国电建集团昆明勘测设计研究院有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">水电站建设；环境影响评价；社会影响评价；ESG</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hydropower station construction, Environmental Impact Assessment, Social Impact Assessment, ESG</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018年8月，中国首例野生动物保护预防性环境公益诉讼—云南绿孔雀案的开庭，把云南省嘎洒江一级水电站工程推上了风口浪尖。本案例从该电站项目的规划、投资建设，到被起诉叫停，渐次展开一个持续了十几年之久的水力发电建设与人类生态保护的冲突故事。建设工程被迫停工后，该故事的持续风波仍未平息。本案例聚焦水电站建设项目的投资回报、经济效益与人类生态和社会影响的冲突，探讨投资项目的财务回报在面对人类生态价值时的取舍决策问题，以及企业投资风险中可能存在的政策风险和环境风险，从一个新的视角审视社会风险下的公司发展之道。本案例丰富了项目投资决策中的政策风险决策，关注公司投资回报所必须面对的社会责任和法律责任，拓展学生对投资的环境、社会因素进行全面分析能力，以及面对危机的决策能力。本案例也提供了一个国家资本投资项目让步人类生态保护的典型故事。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In August 2018, the first-ever preemptive environmental public interest lawsuit for wildlife protection in China, known as the Yunnan Green Peafowl case, placed the Ga Sa River Hydropower Station project in Yunnan Province in the spotlight. This case unfolds a long-standing conflict between hydropower development and human ecological conservation, starting from the planning and investment of the power station project to its suspension due to legal action. Despite the forced halt of construction, the ongoing controversy surrounding the project remains unresolved. This case study focuses on the conflict between the financial returns and economic benefits of hydropower development projects and their impacts on human ecology and society. It explores the decision-making process of balancing financial returns against the value of human ecology, as well as the potential policy and environmental risks within investment ventures. Through this new perspective, it examines the path of corporate development under social risks. The case study enriches the understanding of policy risk assessment in investment decision-making, highlights the social and legal responsibilities that companies must face regarding investment returns, and enhances students&#39; ability to comprehensively analyze environmental and social factors in investment ventures while making decisions in times of crisis. Additionally, this case presents a typical story of a national capital investment project compromising human ecological conservation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》、《公司战略与风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG理论；环境影响评价；社会影响评价；利益相关者理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-11</td>
                            </tr>
